1. On se nalazi u teškom* stanju. (He is in a difficult state.) 
2. Ona je doživela ozbiljne posledice usled njenog stanja*. (She suffered serious consequences due to her condition.) 
3. Svi se nadamo da će ono biti u boljem* stanju. (We all hope that it will be in a better state.) 
4. Lekar je rekao da je njen zdravstveno stanje* zadovoljavajuće. (The doctor said that her health condition is satisfactory.) 
5. On je uspešno preživeo stanje* kome je bio izložen. (He survived the state he was exposed to successfully.)